      "writtenOn": "2020-01-08T22:54:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I thought the check of ctxStreaming.Done() should have guaranteed that. But then I recalled that \"A select blocks until one of its cases can run, then it executes that case. It chooses one at random if multiple are ready.\" \n\nSo the update has been made.",
      "parentUuid": "fd1980d0_ba19de92",
